        "title": "refactor: route bundled session helpers through accessor",
        "body": "## What\n\nRoutes bundled plugin session consumers and SDK/runtime session helper APIs through the narrow session accessor seam while preserving the deprecated file-backed whole-store compatibility helpers.\n\n## Why\n\nThis is part of Path 3 SQLite branch-by-abstraction work. The bundled plugin consumers needed narrow session entry access so SQLite validation can exercise the accessor seam without introducing a mutable SQLite whole-store JSON API.\n\nRefs #88838.\n\n## Changes\n\n- Route SDK session helpers\n- Route plugin runtime helpers\n- Migrate bundled session callers\n- Add lifecycle cleanup seam\n- Preserve file-backed compatibility\n- Cover accessor regressions\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/plugin-sdk/session-store-runtime.ts` | Routes narrow SDK helpers through accessor |\n| `src/plugin-sdk/config-runtime.ts` | Routes config session reads through accessor |\n| `src/plugins/runtime/runtime-agent.ts` | Exposes narrow runtime session helpers |\n| `src/plugins/runtime/types-core.ts` | Adds runtime helper types |\n| `src/config/sessions/session-accessor.ts` | Adds lifecycle cleanup exports |\n| `src/config/sessions/store.ts` | Adds cleanup implementation support |\n| `extensions/discord/src/monitor/*` | Migrates model/thread session paths |\n| `extensions/telegram/src/*` | Migrates model/session metadata reads |\n| `extensions/whatsapp/src/auto-reply/*` | Migrates group activation entry paths |\n| `extensions/memory-core/src/dreaming-narrative.ts` | Uses lifecycle cleanup seam |\n| `extensions/{feishu,matrix,mattermost,slack,codex}` | Uses narrowed session projections |\n| `src/plugin-sdk/*test.ts`, `src/plugins/runtime/index.test.ts` | Adds regression coverage |\n\n## Testing\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/plugin-sdk/config-runtime.test.ts src/plugin-sdk/session-store-runtime.test.ts src/plugins/runtime/index.test.ts extensions/discord/src/monitor/native-command.model-picker.test.ts extensions/discord/src/monitor/thread-session-close.test.ts extensions/telegram/src/bot.create-telegram-bot.test.ts extensions/telegram/src/bot-native-commands.session-meta.test.ts extensions/whatsapp/src/auto-reply/monitor/group-activation.test.ts extensions/memory-core/src/dreaming-narrative.test.ts extensions/active-memory/index.test.ts`\n- Expected: 8 focused file-backed shards pass.\n- Disposable SQLite replay proof is green on `integration/sqlite-flip-bundled-plugin-consumers-replay` after `.18.1`, `.25`, `.26`, and `.10` validation; `.10` is closed in Pebbles.\n- `git diff --check`\n- Targeted formatter/lint/type/autoreview proof was recorded in the Path 3 progress log for this slice.\n",
